data.description:
Modern Elegance in The Shores: 4 Bed, 4 Bath Condo with Updated Features.
Indulge in the perfect blend of modern luxury and low-maintenance living with this impeccably updated 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom condo nestled in the highly desirable community of The Shores. From the moment you step inside, you'll be captivated by the seamless fusion of style and comfort.

The heart of this home is the updated kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances and granite counters—a chef's dream that combines functionality with sophistication. The large modern tiles on the first level create a sleek and inviting ambiance, complemented by a convenient half bath for guests.

Outside is a private oasis with a fenced backyard off the eat-in kitchen, providing the perfect setting for al fresco dining or a morning coffee. The open floorplan effortlessly connects the kitchen to the living room, creating a welcoming space for both relaxation and entertainment.

Upstairs you’ll discover three bedrooms and three bathrooms, including a primary bedroom with its own en-suite bathroom. The thoughtful layout ensures privacy and convenience for every member of the household.

The lower level of this condo unveils a spacious game room area in the basement, offering endless possibilities for entertainment and recreation. Additionally, there’s a non-conforming bedroom and a 3/4 bathroom.

Enjoy the benefits of low-maintenance living in a home that exceeds expectations. Conveniently located near the Tech Center, trails, Highline Canal, shopping, and renowned Cherry Creek schools, this property offers the ideal combination of accessibility and tranquility.

Don't miss the chance to experience the essence of contemporary living in The Shores. Schedule a showing today and imagine the possibilities of calling this updated condo your new home.


******ASSUMABLE VA LOAN AT 3.125 *****(UPAID BALLANCE IS 320,000
